WWE Smackdown kicks off with Cody Rhodes cutting a promo acknowledging his potential competition.

## **_“WHO THE HELL TOLD YOU IT WAS OPEN MIC NIGHT, BITCH?!'“_**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/72f1291b-e12a-441e-87a8-b5f94f0eb188/20240412_171418.jpg?format=original)

Cody now owns the champion locker room, which used to belong to the Bloodline. They try to enter and get rejected by Kevin Owens

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1bf535b5-71e6-49d8-b83d-086d47c836db/20240412_171937.jpg?format=original)

Sheamus returns on RAW next week!

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/400214e4-142c-4b95-a4a9-4e2aad4e5ff0/20240412_172150.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WWE CHAMPIONSHIP #1 CONTENDERS TRIPLE THREAT: BOBBY LASHLEY VS LA KNIGHT VS SANTOS ESCOBAR_**
    

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/38315a01-3516-4699-a6a7-454affb11e7b/Screenshot_20240412_173148.jpg?format=original)

Great triple threat. Lots of chaos with Street Profits and Leagua de Fantasma getting involved at points.

## **_WINNER AND MOVING ON TO THE FINALS: LA KNIGHT_**

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e5832098-55f2-4a14-9eff-01c4255fc873/Screenshot_20240412_174637.jpg?format=original)

Paul Heyman cuts a promo saying the Bloodline takes responsibility for the loss on Sunday.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/37db97ac-6b01-4f4f-8cb2-4ba13a298bf6/20240412_174703.jpg?format=original)

## **_SOLO SIKOA HAS TAKEN OVER THE BLOODLINE BY FORCE. KICKED OUT JIMMY USO AND BROUGHT IN TAMA TONGA!!!!_**

## **_HEYMAN TRIES TO CALL ROMAN AND GETS HIS PHONE SMASHED!_**

