*   ## _BRON BREAKKER DEF. CAMERON GRIMES IN 2 MINS_
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/10349543-b4ce-4346-89c4-d37f4a589b50/20240412_181607.jpg?format=original)

Bayley cuts a promo thanking the fans and everyone who’s been there for her. She wants to defend against Naomi but Tiffany Stratton comes out with her old NXT Theme music to say she best Naomi and she deserves a shot.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1ceee3df-2e36-499a-895b-565b23d04c25/20240412_181559.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_#1 CONTENDERS MATCH: NAOMI VS TIFFANY STRATTON_**
    

Pretty quick match with no real oomph.

## **_WINNER: NAOMI_**

